A web portal for medical care. 
Seperate windows of patient, doctor, hospital management.
All are given with unique id and passwords. The patients can fill their details regarding his health condition and can rise ticket for emergency assistance.

Advantages:

Patients need not wait for the docter in waiting line.
Hospital wont be crowded.
Online assistance will be provided for patients in emergency.
Patients can choose the surgen/ doctor required based on the problem.
